Project.Describe the data being stored onto File:
The data stored by MOVVA Tech on the Filecoin network primarily includes:

High-precision 3D virtual human model data (including topology structures, texture maps, skeletal rigging, and other engineering files);

Massive motion capture raw data (containing sequential data such as facial expression captures and limb movement trajectories);

AI training datasets (comprising labeled motion sequences and rendered samples generated by computer vision algorithms).
